reviews:
I had read reviews about the possibility of receiving a damaged or non functional screen, but decided to continue and take a risk.

For the money spent, if you receive a screen, this is still the way to go in terms of replacing your touch screen without breaking the bank. The quality of the screen is nowhere near that of an official Iphone, however it's less than $50 bucks and comes with all the necessary tools, so that is a bonus.

My screen did not even turn on, as I put everything back together as needed and eventually tested my broken screen, which still lit up and worked, while the new replacement wouldn't even start.....it happens.

I am returning as soon as possible to try another brand in hopes of better luck, but again, if you receive a working screen, this is still a good way to go due to the low cost.

I would stress one thing, keep the screws organized!!!!!! They are beyond small and have a purpose in their placement, so take your time, organize your space and don't worry. Replacing the screen seems daunting, but it's not terrible, you just have to be careful like with any hardware installation for any other electronic device.
No complaints, Amazon had good pricing for this item compared to other places and the package arrived in good condition.

You have to be careful with maple flavoured items, as sometimes the item is given a huge dosage of sugar and passed off as maple. This was not the case regarding the maple cheerios. Excellent maple flavour with a nice after taste and the expected texture from your typical cheerio.

Box was a little small, but this has become a trend in the cereal world. However, for the price I paid, it was justifiable as other places can sell the same product for almost double.
Purchased as a gift and it was very well received. The individual receiving is about the retire and is weighing their options, enter this great little book and it makes for some great reading.

Purchased as a gift for someone and this little thing just changed everyone's life. The built in Alex feature is primo, as you can remove the burden of having to type almost anything into YouTube or one of the various movie apps. Everything is polished and is essentially plug and play.

Please keep in mind that you will need to subscribe to Prime, Netflix or Disney + if you are interested in using these services. If you are not subscribed to anything, Alexa still allows you to retrieve information or use YouTube free of charge as a default.

All that is missing now is a fair tax rate paid by Jeff Bezos and Amazon and the Firestick will then qualify for 6/5 stars!

Great gift idea, but the overall product felt slightly lighter and more fragile than I thought from the photos on Amazon. The individual who received it loved it, so mission accomplished, but I felt clip and slide may not go the distance in terms of long term use, which was disappointing.

Simple and functional, this book is perfect for young children and adults! The words are complimented with English definitions and are situated in real life scenarios, which I would argue is crucial for the proper development of any new language.

I just purchased this player and opening the package and turning it on was bittersweet at best. The overall look is an eye catcher, as it blends a retro look with the horn into a more contemporary package.

I don't usually return something unless it is broken or missing something, but I just packaged this up to send back.

While the horn speaker is a conversation piece, its functionality is very poor. The sound is minimal and there is no bass or depth in the speakers included, which makes this unique player sound no better than a dollar store speaker set.

Bluetooth/Aux issues: I tried to hook the unit up to a stronger pair of speakers in order to improve it and find an excuse to live with the horn speaker issues, but the unit was not kind to this.

As soon as I increased the volume while in Aux mode, I noticed that the horn speaker does not turn off....so you have two sources of sound from the same vinyl, which begins to conflict.

I would have loved to keep it, as again it looks very unique and cool, but I either received a defective unit or the horn speaker is just designed too shallow to make it fully functional.

Colourful, easy to complete and does not rely on overly expensive ingredients to put together a meal. If you are a fan of cook books or cooking shows, you have probably encountered a celebrity chef throwing around saffron like its Christmas! Tasty provides a back to the basics, but equally sophisticated cook book that will brighten up your food prep and keep you happy and healthy!

Purchased as a gift for someone and they have already dug in and finished 2 recipes before the holidays even ended.

Alton Brown never fails to entertain, while also educating people on the science behind food. I purchased a few copies as gifts and everyone was happy to receive them. The recipes aren't over the top, they are delicious and if you have watched Alton on YouTube or on television, you know the guy is crazy for food and the science behind yum!

Its candy, its delicious and you will love it.

Just keep in mind that this box does not contain multiple small packages, but comes with 2 plastic packages filled with candy.

I was surprised to see this, but it did not dissuade anyone from having a sugar overdose on these delicious things.

So...overall mission accomplished!

I ordered this to add as a filler to a gift, but failed to realize that it is not an actual pillow, just the cover (My Bad).

Overall, it turned out great, however I do not think it was fully worth the price I paid for it at the time. If it was priced down slightly more, this would be an excellent balance of value and quality.

The person receiving it loved it, so now it is only a matter of time to see how the quality holds up.

This was purchased for a gift as an everyday watch. The product was exactly as described and comes with all documentation and packaging.

We will see if the battery lasts 10 years, but with the dependability of the name and overall presentation, I wouldn't be surprised if it has no problem handling it.

A cable is a cable unless it doesn't work at all. I have had these on my rig for around 1 year now and they are holding up.

The only downside I would argue is their length, since my tower is on the floor, but I have recently adjusted it and have corrected any issues.

If the cable is stretched to the max, you may begin seeing lines or fuzziness on your screen, this is mainly because you need to ensure the cables are connected with some give or else your connection will suffer.

I bought 4 of these for gifts during Christmas and they performed perfect. We tried them out on an electric coil range and the results were perfectly fine.

I usually leave the batter in for around 1 1/2 minutes on each side, which seemed to do the trick for the perfect "fish" pancake. The skillets are well made and while the handle is plastic, it does not take away from the functionality of preparing these very interesting delights.

The product was alright overall, I felt the taste was not as sour as expected. Skittles tend to be very sweet overall, so the flavour did feel more sweet than sour, but they weren't horrible.

Would make an interesting item just for the novelty of it.

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

I bought this as a gift for someone to use while working out. The quality of the sweater was spot on and did not feel cheap. For the price paid, I would argue that the product was worth it, especially if you are looking for a sweater without having to worry about logos or paying a lot of money for something you are going to work out in or lounge around with.

War is war and there is no such thing as heroes.

If you are a fan of the series, you will not be disappointed by this game collection.

Sadly, the online is no longer as active as it once was, but this happens for all games eventually.

I love this tablet and should really be using it more often.

Google Play was an issue for me, as I wanted to put some time killers on this for around the house, but could not find the necessary apps.

I did eventually learn how to add on Google Play, which has made this tablet that much better, as I can now do my Amazon shopping and enjoy some games to distract the mind when needed.

I would recommend this to everyone, as the customization for my Amazon account and the quality of this item are both excellent.

Good value overall, however the antenna cannot pick up every single station available in my area.

I also had to play around with it in order to find the sweet spot in my home, but the package came with enough cord to achieve this.

For an indoor unit, it is functioning as any other unit would.

Purchased as a gift and everyone thought this thing was the coolest.

A little excessive with a speaker inside, but the quality was just about right for the price.

I would purchase again, however more than 1 is not necessary, as this is more of a novelty gift than a functional one.

I had high hopes for this item and while I try and avoid negative reviews, I cannot fully endorse this brush.

The brush is excellent for smaller/narrower grills, as it performs perfectly.

For more standard barbeques however, I find you really have to push the brush from different angles to remove even standard gunk.

4 stars due to the strong construction and lack of bristles, but unfortunately still not perfect for 5.

I purchased this for a young professional as a gift and they loved it.

An excellent price for an "everyday" watch that shows great functionality with a very nice style.

Time100 is easily becoming one of my new favourite watch companies.

This is the only Funk Pop I own.

Needless to say, it is Bob Ross, so having this around the house makes a nice conversation piece and is a constant reminder to not be afraid to show yourself some kindness.

This item has been performing as intended.

The only thing I hope to see in future versions is the ability to somehow cut the power, even via switch.

That would be make this item perfection, as I have been trying to avoid phantom load throughout the home.

Good quality overall.

Size of roll compared to the best value in competition is a little smaller, but still a great substitute if you cannot visit your local Costco and want to add an item onto your larger order.

I will be purchasing these again once my original bulk order finishes up.

I usually try to remain positive about free apps, however Wish was an odd experience for me.

I ended up ordering 2 items with ease, but found the pricing to be misleading in the app itself. While a sale may show one price, you will easily find this price to alter upon checking out, as sellers are usually promoting 1 individual item, while making it appear that all items in the same category were on sale.

This became stale rather quickly, so while I thought the app was providing a good deal, it actually required some work to ensure the items were actually at the sale price.

Then came the quality, which is very simple as you get what you pay for.

Keep and open mind and pay attention to the check out price, as the item you select may not be the sale item attached to the sale price!

I was interested in purchasing egg rings for a while now, since I love making a few eggs in the morning for breakfast. After trying these out for a few times, I find them very easy to use and also very easy to clean, which is a positive for anything related to cooking in the kitchen.

I would advise though, that you make sure your pan/skillet is level or place a small bowl on the ring after the egg is inside. This should help alleviate any running of the yolk from under the ring while the egg begins to cook.

Aside from that, the product was well priced and I feel as if I received great value for this handy little tool.
Legend

review_title: The software from the latest drivers is very cool and the product runs very quiet
reviews: A couple of months in and this card has been very impressive. The software from the latest drivers is very cool and the product runs very quiet. I think it made a loud hum once so far and it was during an explosive event in the game. Aside from that I am able to run a lot of the games I enjoy at max and am very happy with it.

review_title: I bought the box to enjoy with family and friends and then ended up eating ...
reviews: I bought the box to enjoy with family and friends and then ended up eating it all myself. Considering possibly ranking as a 4 star, since they are so good, they will make you fat since you can't just have 5...

review_title: but the author does an excellent job of turning this into something very special
reviews:
At first, you may feel that a conversation about financial planning with your barber seems out of place, but the author does an excellent job of turning this into something very special.

Even after all of these years, the information is simple, direct and with proper care can assist almost anyone with their own financial planning and long term financial goals.

The key is really to just keep it simple!

review_title: as the panels easily act as sails with even the lightest wind
reviews:
Total setup took roughly 4 1/2 hours. Prepare to work with a buddy, as the panels easily act as sails with even the lightest wind. The only downside with the delivery is that some of my panels were bent in, which required a little more work on my end as I adjusted them to fit properly.

I used a concrete base from a previous shed that rusted out, which greatly helped us, as everything lined up beautifully and fell into place. Currently working on anchoring it down to the base and also applying silicon to the base to ensure more protection from water.

I would also recommend picking up some general wax or polish, as you can begin maintaining the shed with a light wax to ensure further rust protection.

Overall, very satisfied with the shed, as the price on Amazon is also much more competitive than the local big box stores and shipping was free!

review_title: It works, I think... I still ...
reviews:
It works, I think...I still have yet to see any dust or collection in the filter.

So either my house is really clean or this thing isn't picking up exactly everything.

review_title: Had to learn how to reprogram it, as the ...
reviews:
Had to learn how to reprogram it, as the apps can change and require maintenance, but this is standard for all android boxes.

Cannot stand the remote though, only reason why its not 5 stars, the remote is a pain.

review_title: Surprisingly good, just can be difficult to maintain image quality ...
reviews: Surprisingly good, just can be difficult to maintain image quality sometimes, but aside from that overall good. If you have a good screen/wall, the picture quality is even better.
Purchased as a gift for a techie and they loved it.
Excellent, price wise is debatable, but overall comfort and quality are there.
Pain in the arse to install, but it is doing an ok job as of now.

review_title: Easy to install and the only thing I have to ...
reviews:
Easy to install and the only thing I have to worry about now if falling in the shower when the music is playing.

They should add a disclaimer for dancing in the shower, just to be safe!~
Complete the job as intended!

review_title: So far so good, I liked the price and it feels right ...
reviews:
So far so good, I liked the price and it feels right in comparison to the item received.

Do not expect miracles from this little gadget, but compared to others I have tried out, this model seems sturdier and more responsive, plus cheaper in price compared to other imitations, so that is a bonus!

review_title: It makes for a nice toy, but even then it could not hold ...
reviews: Device was not as explained and the functionality was lacking. It makes for a nice toy, but even then it could not hold up to what was claimed. I ended up returning it to be safe as it felt very fragile.

review_title: Impressively accurate, material wise I am not sure how ...
reviews: Impressively accurate, material wise I am not sure how well it will hold up over time, but compared to the official items in stores, the pricing cannot be beat. I found something of similar material going for just over double the price, so if you can wait a few weeks for direct from China shipping, it will be worth the investment to your tool arsenal. Just don't hope for miracles in regards to the overall life span of this device, as I don't think it will hold up to extreme use.

review_title: Excellent recipes from an excellent chef
reviews: Excellent recipes from an excellent chef, the book is of high quality and the material is on par. Purchased as a gift and could not be happier!

review_title: Excellent recipes from an excellent chef
reviews: You get what you pay for! Excellent recipes from an excellent chef, very happy with this purchase as it is for gifts and is high quality.

I'm in love with it. A true showcase of premium Japanese watchmanship at a very reasonable price.

The sun/moon dial only makes the watch better.

Only downside is the error with Roman Numeral 4, should read as IV not IIII.
